## 9. Task Workflow
1. Plan first → write it to `tasks/todo.md`
2. Confirm plan with me
3. Check items off as you go
4. Summarize changes at a high level
5. Add a short review to `tasks/todo.md`
6. Capture any lessons in `tasks/lessons.md`

## Final Instruction (for you, Claude)
- When I correct you or you catch your own mistake, update the **Forbidden Patterns** section and append to `tasks/lessons.md`.
- Keep this file short and focused — if it exceeds ~150 lines, move specifics to `.claude/rules/<topic>.md` and import with `@rules/<topic>.md`.
- Use subagents and Plan Mode by default.
